&lt;p&gt;    And set up a Auth es6 class that gonna handle the requests like this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    ```&lt;br/&gt;
    module.exports = class AuthSrv {&lt;br/&gt;
        constructor() &lt;/p&gt;
