&lt;p&gt;    In this scenario, i&apos;m getting that &lt;b&gt;this&lt;/b&gt; pointer is *&lt;b&gt;undefined&lt;/b&gt;* when signin function is called. Looking at thrift generated code for the processor i saw this line:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    ```&lt;br/&gt;
