        .then(.....)
    }
&lt;p&gt;    ```&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    everything works like a charm and &lt;b&gt;this&lt;/b&gt; pointer is correctly assinged inside signin function call.&lt;/p&gt;

